^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|A couple of things to discuss there. First of all, let's look at Roberta's 2C bid. I don't mind it per se, but if she was planning to rebid 2N, she should open 2N to start with because her auction shows 22-24, and she only has 21. My question is, suppose you opened 2C and I bid 2D, what was your next bid going to be?|
